sequenceDiagram
    participant SDK as Pipeline Component<br/>(Python SDK)
    participant Server as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP

    Note over SDK,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Metadata Recording

    SDK->>Server: PutExecution / PutArtifacts / PutEvents<br/>gRPC/8080 | Optional TLS | Optional mTLS
    Server->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE metadata<br/>TCP/5432 | Optional SSL | Password Auth
    DB-->>Server: Query Result
    Server-->>SDK: PutExecutionResponse<br/>gRPC | Optional TLS

    Note over SDK,DB: Flow 2: Lineage Graph Query

    participant UI as DSP UI / API Client

    UI->>Server: GetLineageSubgraph<br/>gRPC/8080 | Optional TLS | Optional mTLS
    Server->>DB: SELECT lineage data<br/>TCP/5432 | Optional SSL | Password Auth
    DB-->>Server: Lineage Result Set
    Server-->>UI: LineageSubgraph Response<br/>gRPC | Optional TLS

    Note over SDK,DB: Flow 3: Type Registration (Pipeline Setup)

    SDK->>Server: PutArtifactType / PutExecutionType<br/>gRPC/8080 | Optional TLS
    Server->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE type schema<br/>TCP/5432 | Optional SSL
    DB-->>Server: Type ID
    Server-->>SDK: PutArtifactTypeResponse (type_id)

    Note over SDK,DB: Flow 4: Artifact Retrieval by Context

    SDK->>Server: GetArtifactsByContext<br/>gRPC/8080 | Optional TLS
    Server->>DB: SELECT artifacts JOIN attributions<br/>TCP/5432 | Optional SSL
    DB-->>Server: Artifact Records
    Server-->>SDK: GetArtifactsByContextResponse
